      "role": "user",
      "content": "small steps just feel like more weight to carry. i'm just so tired of existing like this. sometimes i sit here and think that the only way to actually stop the ache, the only way to truly get some rest, is to just... let go of everything entirely. it feels like the only way to find any peace at all.",
